sources.description:
Grace and Goliath - Hollywood big shot Josh Jenkins sweeps into Belfast to make a movie, but before long his world crashes and he loses everything. Hotel cleaner Lily invites him to stay with her crazy family and gradually the people of this `strange' city touch his heart forever.
2018.  Stars: Emy Aneke, Tommy Bowe, Maria Brashier
